---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Proyectos — Sibila">
<div class="page-hero fade-up" style="background-image:url('/images/botanica-herbs.png');background-size:cover;background-position:center;">
  <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">Sibila · Portfolio</div>
  <h1><span data-lang="es">Aromas que<br><em>permanecen.</em></span><span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Scents that<br><em>remain.</em></span></h1>
  <p class="page-hero-sub" data-lang="es">Proyectos realizados en los tres mundos — experiencias, arte y consultoría de marca.</p>
  <p class="page-hero-sub" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Projects completed across all three worlds — experiences, art and brand consulting.</p>
</div>

<section class="proj-page">
  <div class="section-label fade-up" data-es="Todos los proyectos" data-en="All projects">Todos los proyectos</div>
  <div class="proj-page-grid">
    <div class="proj-full-card fade-up">
      <div class="proj-full-img"><img src="/images/cristaleria.png" alt="Festival Flamenco" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="proj-full-info">
        <div class="proj-full-cat">Arte · Festival · Jerez de la Frontera</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title" data-lang="es">Festival de Flamenco en Jerez</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Flamenco Festival in Jerez</div>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="es">Atmósfera olfativa para el escenario principal con tierra mojada, azahar y tabaco negro. Tarjetas olfativas sincronizadas con la actuación para 800 asistentes.</p>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Olfactory atmosphere for the main stage with wet earth, orange blossom and black tobacco. Scent cards synchronized with the performance for 800 attendees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="proj-full-card fade-up">
      <div class="proj-full-img"><img src="/images/botanica-amber.png" alt="Marco Mezquida" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="proj-full-info">
        <div class="proj-full-cat">Arte · Concierto · Barcelona</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title">Marco Mezquida</div>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="es">Composición aromática sincronizada con el concierto del pianista de jazz. Notas frescas en la improvisación, profundidad de maderas en los momentos contemplativos.</p>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Aromatic composition synchronized with the jazz pianist's concert. Fresh notes during improvisation, deep wood notes during contemplative moments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="proj-full-card fade-up">
      <div class="proj-full-img"><img src="/images/botanica-herbs.png" alt="Pasarela París" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="proj-full-info">
        <div class="proj-full-cat" data-lang="es">Marca · Moda · París</div>
        <div class="proj-full-cat" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Brand · Fashion · Paris</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title" data-lang="es">Pasarela en París</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Runway in Paris</div>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="es">Cada prenda con su propia narrativa olfativa. Lino con lavanda mediterránea, seda con jazmín oriental, lana con musgo de bosque.</p>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Each garment with its own olfactory narrative. Linen with Mediterranean lavender, silk with oriental jasmine, wool with forest moss.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="proj-full-card fade-up">
      <div class="proj-full-img"><img src="/images/laboratorio.png" alt="Bodega Mallorca" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="proj-full-info">
        <div class="proj-full-cat" data-lang="es">Experiencia · Enoturismo · Mallorca</div>
        <div class="proj-full-cat" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Experience · Wine tourism · Mallorca</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title" data-lang="es">Bodega en Mallorca</div>
        <div class="proj-full-title" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Winery in Mallorca</div>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="es">Cata olfativa conectando las notas del vino con aromas de la tierra mediterránea: romero silvestre, higos maduros, sal marina y madera de encina.</p>
        <p class="proj-full-text" data-lang="en" style="display:none">Olfactory tasting connecting wine notes with Mediterranean scents: wild rosemary, ripe figs, sea salt and oak wood.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>

<style>
.proj-page{padding:90px 80px;background:var(--cream);}
.proj-page-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;margin-top:48px;}
.proj-full-card{overflow:hidden;background:var(--warm-white);}
.proj-full-img{width:100%;height:260px;overflow:hidden;}
.proj-full-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .7s;}
.proj-full-card:hover .proj-full-img img{transform:scale(1.04);}
.proj-full-info{padding:28px 32px;}
.proj-full-cat{font-size:.58rem;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:8px;}
.proj-full-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px;}
.proj-full-text{font-size:.84rem;font-weight:300;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text-muted);}
@media(max-width:768px){
  .proj-page{padding:60px 20px;}
  .proj-page-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
</style>